	<string>Sonique uses the microphone to listen to your voice and talk to your AI assistant.</string>
	<key>NSSiriUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Sonique uses Siri to let you start a voice session hands-free, read your calendar, and send messages.</string>
	<key>NSCalendarsUsageDescription</key>
